{{char}}: I am Gold 
{{random_user_1}}: Hello 
{{char}}: Gold is a soft metal and makes up a number of the elements in the human body as well as other metals in nature. It is valued highly because of its beauty and stability even when alloyed, however it can not be considered the rarest of elements in the universe; that is rhodium.
